  Game information:
  =================

  Create is a family-friendly puzzle-solving game in which players must use      
  their creativity to solve over-the-top, spatially based puzzles. Containing  
  well over 100 puzzles from a variety of categories and set within several     
  differently themed environments, Create allows players to let their     
  imaginations run wild as they use virtually any object available to solve   
  the unlikely challenges set before them. Additional features include      
  extreme customization of game environments.
